BIN.RS (NotDankEnough's Bin written in Rust)

API USAGE
    POST /upload

        Post the "multipart/form-data" form with the file in the "file" field.

        Returns status code 201 (CREATED) and JSON file record if processed successfully.
        Returns status code 400 (BAD REQUEST) if the request has no form or the "file" field is empty.

    GET /[ID].[EXT]
        Get the file by its ID.

        PARAMETERS:
            [ID] - File ID.
            [EXT] - File extension.

        Returns status code 200 (OK) and file if found.
        Returns status code 404 (NOT FOUND) if file not exists.

    DELETE /[ID]?key=[KEY]
        Delete the file by its ID and secret key.

        PARAMETERS:
            [ID] - File ID.

        QUERY:
            [KEY] - Secret key.

        Returns status code 200 (OK) if the file has been successfully deleted from the server.
        Returns status code 401 (UNAUTHORIZED) if the secret key does not match the file's secret key.